08:30.293 --> 08:31.712
- Still impressive.
- Thank you.

08:31.795 --> 08:35.215
Plus, I feel like I just got a window
into the life of 14-year-old Gus.

08:35.298 --> 08:36.299
Yikes!

08:39.010 --> 08:40.136
Gus Cru-shek?

08:41.011 --> 08:42.806
- Oh, right here.
- Hey.

08:43.306 --> 08:45.851
