09:53.836 --> 09:54.962
- Your nephew?
- [gasps]

09:55.045 --> 09:56.815
- You don't remember your nephew's name?
- Oh, okay.

09:56.839 --> 09:58.519
In my defense, he's, like,
three years old,

09:58.548 --> 10:00.550
