12:13.475 --> 12:16.144
How did you meet, uh...
What's his name?

12:16.228 --> 12:17.437
- Dustin.
- Dustin.

12:17.520 --> 12:19.064
He used to manage my friend's band.

12:19.648 --> 12:22.025
- That's cool.
- Yeah, I thought so, too.

12:22.109 --> 12:25.445
